@startuml audio_focus_to_vcs_tts_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Audio Focus To VCS TTS Signal Flow\n(audio focus + TMU service + cluster notif -> VCS voice/TTS publish)

participant "Audio focus / TMU /\ncluster notification inputs" as VoiceCtx #F4F7FB
participant "VCS\nvoice control owner" as VCS #E8F7E8
participant "Voice / TTS state bus" as VoiceBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers / audio users" as Obs #E8F0FE

== Voice Inputs ==

VoiceCtx -> VCS : audioFocusOwner / audioDuckingLvl\ntmuServiceMode / signalBars\nclusterNotifType / clusterNotifArg
VCS -> VCS : if audio focus stale\nthen focusOwner = 0 / duck = 0
VCS -> VCS : if TMU stale\nthen serviceMode = 0 / bars = 0
VCS -> VCS : if notif stale\nthen notifType = 0 / notifArg = 0
VCS -> VCS : voiceAssistState from serviceMode / focusOwner
VCS -> VCS : wakeWordState when serviceMode == 1 and bars >= 2
VCS -> VCS : ttsState / ttsPriority / ttsQueueDepth from notif + focus + duck
note right of VCS
Representative gating inputs
- audioFocusOwner / audioDuckingLvl
- tmuServiceMode / signalBars
- clusterNotifType / clusterNotifArg
end note

== Voice Publish ==

VCS -> VoiceBus : frmVoiceAssistStateMsg\nVoiceAssistState / WakeWordState
VCS -> VoiceBus : frmSpeechTtsStateMsg\nTtsState / TtsPriority / TtsQueueDepth
note right of VCS
Representative outputs
- VoiceAssistState
- WakeWordState
- TtsState / Priority / QueueDepth
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

VoiceBus -> Obs : voice/TTS readback /\naudio-routing consumers

note over VoiceCtx, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Audio focus, TMU, and notification context reach VCS
2. VCS determines assist, wake-word, and TTS activity
3. VCS publishes voice and TTS state frames
4. Audio users and observers consume the effective spoken-output posture
end note

@enduml
